title: SPACE FORCE Ending Explained!
author: Think Story
comment: Back from a break! Hoping to cover a ton of new shows and movies in June. Stay tuned!
STILL no one is talking about why his wife is in jail though
I liked the show, I don't know why it's getting so much critcism

I recently finished the show and I have to say it has soooo much potential, and to anyone considering watching to give it a chance. It’s got a good batch of flaws for sure, and the first few episodes move slowly, but it comes along later in the season and becomes quite a charming show in my opinion. It’s no masterpiece but I think it has a LOT of potential. Look at the office- the first season was pretty boring aside from a few good scenes, I hope they give this show a chance to find it’s wings because I can tell it would be really great if given the opportunity.
I like it. It's got some heart.
description:
In this video we take a deep dive and explain the ending to Netflix and Greg Daniel's latest comedy series SPACE FORCE starring Steve Carell. We'll review, recap, and break down the ending to season 1.
